The '''spectacled tetraka''' ('''''Xanthomixis zosterops''''') is a [[species]] of [[Malagasy warbler]] in the family [[Malagasy warbler|Bernieridae]].  It is found only in [[Madagascar]].  Its natural [[habitat]] is [[subtropical]] or [[tropical]] moist lowland [[forest]]s.

